=== 冲突 ===
按照德利奇的说法，4月23日凌晨5时45分，第549机动旅第53边境营的士兵在科沙雷哨所附近遇到了一群150至200名武装分子，他们试图通过代查尼以西的北阿尔巴尼亚非法进入科索沃。<ref name="ICTY">{{cite web|publisher=ICTY|title=The Prosecutor vs. Slobodan Milošević — Božidar Delić Testimony|url=http://www.icty.org/x/cases/slobodan_milosevic/trans/en/050622IT.htm|date=2005-06-22|access-date=2015-08-13|pages=9377–91|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122051937/https://www.icty.org/x/cases/slobodan_milosevic/trans/en/050622IT.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>反政府武装已经在阿尔巴尼亚和南斯拉夫边境集结了一段时间，期待着南斯拉夫军再次发动进攻。<ref name="CT1">{{cite web|publisher=Chicago Tribune|title=New Fighting Breaks Out As Serbs Vote On Kosovo|author=Guy Dinmore|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-04-24/news/9804240087_1_foreign-mediation-kosovo-albanian-yugoslav-forces|date=1998-04-24|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095908/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-04-24/news/9804240087_1_foreign-mediation-kosovo-albanian-yugoslav-forces|dead-url=no}}</ref>南斯拉夫当局说，这些武装分子是“武装渗透者”，他们在阿尔巴尼亚的军事营地接受训练，<ref name="BBC">{{cite web|publisher=BBC|title=Serb 'no' to foreign mediation in Kosovo|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1998/kosovo/82713.stm|date=1998-04-24|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115192005/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1998/kosovo/82713.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN">{{cite web |publisher=CNN |title=16 reported killed in clashes as Serbs vote on Kosovo |url=http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/europe/9804/23/yugo.referendum.update/index.html |date=1998-04-24 |access-date=2015-08-13 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051109212211/http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/europe/9804/23/yugo.referendum.update/index.html |archive-date=2005-11-09 }}</ref>企图向科索沃走私武器。<ref name="CNN1">{{cite web|publisher=CNN|title=EU imposes new arms sanctions on Yugoslavia|url=http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/europe/9804/27/kosovo.folos/index.html|date=1998-04-27|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134820/http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/europe/9804/27/kosovo.folos/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CT2">{{cite web|publisher=Chicago Tribune|title=Albanians Bury 9 As Clashes Rage In Kosovo|author=Guy Dinmore|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-04-28/news/9804280230_1_albanian-kosovo-liberation-army-yugoslav-army|date=1998-04-28|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100121/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-04-28/news/9804280230_1_albanian-kosovo-liberation-army-yugoslav-army|dead-url=no}}</ref>按照德利奇的说法，武装分子在人数上远远超过了边境巡逻队。<ref name="ICTY"/>配备榴弹炮和火箭发射器的巡逻队伏击了该武装组织，<ref name="CNN"/>引发了激烈交火。<ref name="ICTY"/>据报道，冲突持续了一整夜，科索沃边界村庄巴图斯的阿族居民报告说，第二天有炮火和[[直升飞机|直升飞机]]飞过头顶。<ref name="NYT">{{cite web|work=The New York Times|title=23 Albanians Killed in Clashes With Yugoslav Troops in Kosovo|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/24/world/23-albanians-killed-in-clashes-with-yugoslav-troops-in-kosovo.html|date=1998-04-24|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123000248/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/24/world/23-albanians-killed-in-clashes-with-yugoslav-troops-in-kosovo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

南斯拉夫军在冲突中没有人员伤亡。<ref name="CT1"/><ref name="CNN"/>19名武装分子被打死，<ref name="CT2"/>1人受伤，<ref name="CNN"/>另外2人被捕。<ref name="CNN"/><ref name="AP">{{citation|publisher=Associated Press|title=Yugoslavia warns of war|date=1998-04-24}}</ref>这是自上个月贾沙里的院舍遭到[[进攻普雷卡齐|袭击]]以来，科索沃所发生最致命的战争相关事件。<ref name="NYT"/><ref name="LAT1">{{cite web|work=Los Angeles Times|title=Yugoslav Army Warns West Over Kosovo|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/25/news/mn-42834|date=1998-04-25|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307041225/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/25/news/mn-42834|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LAT">{{cite web|work=Los Angeles Times|title=Up to 23 Ethnic Albanians Slain, Serb Officials Say|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/24/news/mn-42612|date=1998-04-24|access-date=2015-08-13|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307130527/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/24/news/mn-42612|dead-url=no}}</ref>初步报告显示，有16到23名武装分子被杀。<ref name="BBC"/><ref name="CNN"/><ref name="LAT"/>其中9名被击毙的武装分子来自位于代查尼附近的埃里克村，这里距离阿尔巴尼亚边境约{{convert|9.7|km}}。<ref name="CT2"/>德利奇确认被俘的武装分子分别是加兹门德·塔希拉伊（来自埃里克的英语教授）和伊伯尔·梅塔伊（来自埃里克的农业技术员）。据德利奇报道，剩余的武装分子要么成功突破了伏击，抵达科索沃，要么逃回阿尔巴尼亚。<ref name="ICTY"/>由军方拍摄、后来在南斯拉夫电视台播出的画面显示，战场上散落着枪支、弹药和三名武装分子的尸体。<ref name="AP"/>南斯拉夫军报告缴获{{convert|4|tonnes}}武器和[[弹药|弹药]]，包括120箱[[地雷|地雷]]。<ref>{{cite news|publisher=Detroit Free Press|title=Yugoslav army ambush keeps armed Albanians from Kosovo|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/99853894/?terms=Kosovo%2Bambush|date=1998-04-27|access-date=2016-03-19|via=Newspapers.com|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117191831/https://www.newspapers.com/image/99853894/?terms=Kosovo%2Bambush|dead-url=no}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

=== 后果 ===
